snippet.title: Among Us Livestream! WHO IS THE IMPOSTER? Feat. Outside Xbox and Dicebreaker
snippet.description:
In space, no-one can hear you stream. Luke is joined by Andy and Mike from Outside Xbox, and Johnny and Alex from Dicebreaker for social stealth game Among Us.

Subscribe to Dicebreaker: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0jMXccxfvnwXvTpngFwbNA

---

Official Merch Store! https://teespring.com/stores/outside-xbox-outside-xtra

Become a member of Outside Xtra! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjf6YzmyaKi8880IXMJ5kGA/join

Outside Xtra is a companion channel to Outside Xbox, covering the wider world of gaming with weekly lists, Let's Plays and shows with your hosts Ellen and Luke. Look for regular appearances by OG Outside Xboxers Andy, Jane and Mike, and generally more of the videos you love, about more of the platforms you enjoy, from a team now two people larger overall.

Thanks for watching and be excellent to each other in the comments.

Find us at http://www.outsidextra.com
Subscribe to us at http://www.youtube.com/outsidextra
Like us on Facebook at http://www.facebook.com/outsidextra
Follow us on Twitter at http://www.twitter.com/outsidextra
